description:
Rory Kramer, THE photo & video don, has been the creative director for Justin Bieber, The Chainsmokers, Avicii, and more. Recently engaged, he’s boxed Justin Bieber, travelled all over the world, and nearly lost his life in a horrifying car accident. Also, Logan reveals how he got his penis stuck in a pogo stick.
